        * m4/lib-link.m4: Upgrade to gettext-0.17.
        * m4/po.m4: Upgrade to gettext-0.17.
        * m4/intdiv0.m4: Upgrade to gettext-0.17.
        * m4/intl.m4: Upgrade to gettext-0.17.
