        * src/buf.c:
        * src/ed.h:
        * src/main.c: Clean up #include's.

2006-12-06  Andrew L. Moore  <alm@slewsys.org>

        * src/exec.c (exec_command): Remove redundant call to
        clear_undo_stack ().

        * src/cmds.c (display_lines):
        * src/exec.c (GET_THIRD_ADDR):
        (exec_command):
        (get_shell_command):
